WEBVTT

00:01.871 --> 00:04.091
So, if Rex Huntington
is the finest doctor

00:04.178 --> 00:05.483
in Spring Valley, why is he

00:05.570 --> 00:06.832
defending Jessica
in the murder trial?

00:06.919 --> 00:08.573
Because, before
he got pushed

00:08.660 --> 00:10.271
off the mountain
and got amnesia,

00:10.358 --> 00:12.403
he was the finest lawyer
in Spring Valley.

00:12.490 --> 00:13.796
What I can't believe

00:13.883 --> 00:15.232
is Jessica is having
an affair with the judge.

00:15.319 --> 00:17.191
I mean, he's
totally using her

00:17.278 --> 00:20.020
to get his hands
on the Farnsworth fortune.

00:20.107 --> 00:21.369
You can't ground me!

00:21.456 --> 00:23.371
That fire could have
been started by anybody!

00:23.458 --> 00:24.894
Why don't you
ever take my side?!

00:24.981 --> 00:26.461
You never listen
anything I say!

00:29.812 --> 00:30.726
You know, Reese,

00:30.813 --> 00:32.162
some very manly men

00:32.249 --> 00:34.121
watch soap operas
With their mothers.

